# If the Superintendent of Schools has reason to suspect that a fraud has occurred, he or she will notify the District's Attorney, State of Connecticut Troopers, and the Business Manager and/or insurance company.
# The alleged fraud or audit investigation shall not be discussed with the media by any person other than the Superintendent of Schools, State of Connecticut Resident Trooper or his/her designee, or the District's Attorney.
